"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        VVIR",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        Fixed atrial arrhythmias (atrial fibrillation or flutter) with symptomatic bradycardia in the chronotropically incompetent patient",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        As for VVI",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        As for VVI",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        AAI",
